---
title: Roasted Eggplant Risotto with Parmesan Cheese & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish
description: Eggplant and carrot, roasted to golden perfection, are tossed through a herby risotto. You’ll notice the sharp Parmesan coming
through and the chargrilled capsicum relish really elevates this dinner to the next level. Finish it off with toasty almonds for a nutty flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

